        <head xml:id="la30px-aaa981-Hd1e104">Proposition 20</head>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa981-d1e106"> Proposition 20 </p>
        <p xml:id="la30px-aaa981-d1e111">
          The kings of Castilla are obligated by the formal
          instruction of the Apostolic See, and also by divine law, to diligently provide and send
          ideal ministers to preach the faith throughout the whole New World. These ministers are to
          call and invite the peoples of this world, so that they might come to the weddings and
          feast of Christ, and to everything else said in Proposition II which is done in order to
          achieve this end.
        </p>
